channel.title: New Kalphites + NPC of the Week!
channel.description:
[b]Hello.[/b]
[size=75pt]COMMENT![/size]
[b]What Ive Fixed on my Old kalphite Queen :[/b]
[ul][li]Added Second Form. Its 100% Like RS only no Working Attack emotes & Dieing Emotes.[/li] [li]Made Standing Emote of Both Queens 1150. Emote 1150 will Fix the Elastic Standing Emotes.[/li] [li]Added Worker,Soldier & Guardian to. They are Bugged So dont laugh LOL.[/li][/ul]
[b]Hope you Like the Monster of the Week.[/b]
The Guardian is Most Bugged. Very Elastic & its very Big. ( Bigger then Queen LOL )
Lets Start With the Kalphite Worker : ( Bugged ) [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img401.imageshack.us/img401/6443/workerbm7.jpg[/img][/URL] Very Easy to Code. it only has 1 Model so i didnt was Like Zomg Thats hard. The Second Form queen Was abit jeezy to Add. I Didnt know all Models and it had 3 models to make it full.
The Soldier! ( Bugged ) : [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img407.imageshack.us/img407/6791/soldiertp5.jpg[/img][/URL]
Lets Show You the most Bugged NPC I ever seen. : [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img407.imageshack.us/img407/3254/guardianvj1.jpg[/img][/URL]
The Queen! ( 1st Form ) : [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img45.imageshack.us/img45/8941/kqueen1sr9.jpg[/img][/URL]
Now You Will be Like Zomg!! Nice QUEEN!!! But if you see this. I Hope you Enjoy my Lasted Updated Queen.
Kalphite Queen Second Form! [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img45.imageshack.us/img45/922/kqueen2yc8.jpg[/img][/URL]
Monster of the Week! NON BUGGED! [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img407.imageshack.us/img407/1452/monsterweekdr1.jpg[/img][/URL]
Enjoy Cache Editing.
